{"tid":1435834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只知道一哥失了蹤，不知道鄉黑這麼勇","createTime":"2019-08-09T06:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T07:20:16.000Z","uid":260372,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"934cf0a10e7c5b95bcffdc0f7022b638faeb7461","tid":1435834,"uid":260372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:59:49.000Z","msg":"挑機再扑爆 然後不相信<br />\n<br />\n從你眼中 找到了郁手幾秒鐘<br />\n<br />\n只不過期望已經不同<br />\n<br />\n源自警黑勾結太盡<br />\n<br />\n誰若抽身我反送中 不送<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=358488&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358488%26refer%3DShare&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=88263d28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358488%26refer%3DShare&h=402dddb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=358488&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】警務處前副處長劉業成獲委任為臨時警務處副處長。<br />\n<br />\n劉業成獲委任為臨時警務處副處長，即日生效，主要協助警務處處長處理大型公眾活動及策劃未來多項大型行動，包括國慶70周年相關慶祝活動等。<br />\n<br />\n57歲的劉業成於去年11月開始退休前休假，曾先後調任多個政策部及行動部門，處理包括2005年世貿韓農示威及2014年佔領活動等。<br />\n<br />\n連同另外兩位警務處副處長鄧炳強及郭蔭庶，是回歸以來警隊首次同時有三名副處長。"},{"pid":"c4192fb040f6a992b19f8e494d8a0512db227c6c","tid":1435834,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:01:01.000Z","msg":"問佢點解釋721啦咁"},{"pid":"fcf031fcaf74b709374f18162ecf9ced702ed577","tid":1435834,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"只知道警察失了蹤<br />\n會唔會啱音少少"},{"pid":"111885bc1182af0ee48fdefaedf54c35e8584310","tid":1435834,"uid":191688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:19:17.000Z","msg":"開返個五毛回覆範本有冇得諗？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435787</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b43bb46cffd9288